reviewBody:
I have been unwell this last week and added unnecessary stress upon myself regarding my studies.

David Cox contacted me to see how I was getting on and within minutes Saraya Morgan contacted me.

Saraya actively listened to me; 
she was empathic and acknowledged my anxieties and concerns;
Saraya gave me advice and guidance which has reduced my anxieties and her approach, manner and exceptional customer service skills has not only reassured me that I can do this course but Saraya has ignited my passion to continue studying.

Thank you Saraya Morgan, David Cox and the Learn Direct Team!
